race.comment: TURNED DOWN (3) was game when resuming at Bathurst over 1300m, racing on speed before fading late into fourth. Strips fitter and should be in the firing line again. FETES DES MERES (4) has put together two strong placings, most recently a narrow second over this journey at Mudgee. Winning hoop in Grima reunites and can add to the tally. RHYTHM IS A DANCER (1) scored two back at Mudgee but wasn't at his best last start at Gunnedah. Can bounce back. EPIC POEM (6) was well held first-up but fitter now and capable of sharp improvement on quick turnaround. STARLINK (5) can contest for a place and may add some value.
